version_description: - iPhone 6 and iPhone 6 Plus compatibility fixes.

- 64-bit support
- Facebook Messenger export support
- Bug fixes and performance improvements
Special discount - 50% off Facetune 2 subscriptions of any kind, for all our loyal Facetune users!
Bug fixes.
Improved supported resolution - 16MP editing on iPhone 7 / 7 Plus, iPhone 6s / 6s Plus and iPhone SE
Bug fix - Wide color images can now be imported and edited as regular images.
Bug fixes and performance improvements
Bug fixes and performance improvements
Routine maintenance
Routine maintenance
Routine maintenance

We've made some backstage changes in preparation for the next generation of Apple devices and we're excited to see the gorgeous portraits you create when you pair the power of Facetune with the new iPhone X.

Enjoy!
Daniel & The Facetune Team

P.S. If you love Facetune, we'd be thankful if you rated us!

This update includes some fine-tuning to Facetune!

- Metadata saving is back on track
- Fixed a crash when opening the camera
- Fixed a bug related to permissions, you may be asked  for access to your photos

Enjoy!
Daniel & The Facetune Team

Updated settings to comply with the new GDPR policy. As well as some routine maintenance.

Daniel & The Facetune Team

P.S. If you love Facetune, we'd be thankful if you rated us!

Here's what's new in this release

- We now fully support iOS 13

Daniel and The Facetune Team
